ComicInfo.Summary: Your prayers have been answered! Warrior Nun will grace shelves again with an all-new adventure! Experience a brand-new, re-envisioned Warrior Nun! A violent explosion rocks the halls of the Vatican, revealing an alarming plot to attain several ancient, holy relics by a secret society known as The Advent. Charged with the investigation is Sister Isabel, a high-ranking agent of the Order of Crosius, an elite, clandestine group of warriors. The action kicks off as Isabel, with the aid of a sworn enemy, races across the globe to battle the deadly competition and exact savage vengeance.
